	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Those who swear an oath of vengeance choose to hunt down creatures who have wronged others. Sometimes an avenger hunts a specific organization or group of creatures, and sometimes an avenger simply tries to destroy evil. Some avengers become obsessive or selfishly focused on a campaign of vengeance, but usually paladins following this path put protecting others above all else. Avengers are powerful at punishing and locking down foes.</em></p><table><caption><p>The Avenger</p></caption><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\"><p>Level</p></th><th scope=\"col\"><p>Features</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>3</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.wjflquP9J7ItZqny]{Avenger's Leap} or @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.MUXZKqXOk5k1w8pS]{Commanding Challenge}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>6</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.2yjAwCh8FpQP0MAP]{Searing Retribution}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>10</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.wjflquP9J7ItZqny]{Avenger's Leap} or @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.MUXZKqXOk5k1w8pS]{Commanding Challenge}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>14</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.xrqF7vKMSesGLGPq]{Avenger's Vow}</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table><caption><p>Expanded Spell List</p></caption><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\"><p>Paladin Level</p></th><th scope=\"col\"><p>Extra Spells</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>3</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.SZi4TOafYgqm0A0n]{Shadow Strike}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>5</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.5YfzPpLkF7a0VrIq]{Curse of Frailty}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>9</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.q7llCYymIoKel6j0]{Bloodlust}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>13</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.lwtpOJ9KoOjbFkNX]{Locate Creatu